name: Ltd. Edition Print of Artist Christopher Bost - 8"x10"
description:
Printed on archival, museum-grade paper this giclee print is available in two sizes:   8x10 and 13x19.  
This is a signed, limited edition of 33. 

All proceeds from this specially-priced print will fund the Unknown Forces Book project.  

This project is dedicated to showcasing the community of artists, musicians and creative mavericks who live and work in the desert surrounding Joshua Tree, California.  
Through photographic portraits, audio and video interviews.  

The project will culminate with a coffee table-style book and gallery show of ltd edition prints.  A portion of the profits from the resulting book will be used to establish a Joshua Tree-based creative residency.

This is an ongoing project.
